362
00:24:47,071 --> 00:24:49,804
When can you guys move
into the new apartment?

363
00:24:49,804 --> 00:24:52,271
We're closing the deal today,

364
00:24:52,271 --> 00:24:54,804
so we'll be able to start moving
things in next week.

365
00:24:54,804 --> 00:24:57,438
The furniture and appliances
will be delivered next week.

366
00:24:57,438 --> 00:24:59,304
