369
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:04,704
No matter how busy things get.

370
00:25:04,704 --> 00:25:07,970
don't fall behind on your studies
for the certification exam.

371
00:25:07,970 --> 00:25:09,570
I won't.

372
00:25:09,570 --> 00:25:11,570
May I be excused?

373
00:25:17,837 --> 00:25:19,804
Why are you nagging her about
the exam? She looks so tired.

374
00:25:19,804 --> 00:25:21,570
Da Ran,

375
00:25:21,570 --> 00:25:23,970
