379
00:25:32,603 --> 00:25:39,137
Say, how do you and Yun Jae know
Mary, the college girl from the States?

380
00:25:39,137 --> 00:25:40,804
College girl?

381
00:25:40,804 --> 00:25:44,870
No. She's your age.

382
