384
00:25:50,537 --> 00:25:52,837
I should get pizza off the ledger for that.

385
00:25:52,837 --> 00:25:54,204
Oh, right.

386
00:25:54,204 --> 00:25:57,537
She told me to tell you she's deducting
10 pizzas from your debt.

387
00:25:57,537 --> 00:25:58,937
What's that about?

388
00:25:58,937 --> 00:26:00,304
Really?

389
00:26:02,137 --> 00:26:05,704
