You've been like that all day.

407
00:27:46,837 --> 00:27:49,104
Black tea...

408
00:27:49,104 --> 00:27:50,837
Black tea?

409
00:27:50,837 --> 00:27:54,570
No. We managed to close Pandora's Box.

410
00:27:56,704 --> 00:27:58,704
Ms. Gil Da Ran,

411
00:27:58,704 --> 00:28:00,637
I'm visiting Kang Gyeong Jun
at the hospital today.

412
00:28:00,637 --> 00:28:03,071
Would you like me to give you a lift?

413
00:28:03,904 --> 00:28:07,870
Look at how considerate you've become.

414
00:28:07,870 --> 00:28:09,570
Thank you very much,

415
00:28:09,570 --> 00:28:12,570
