417
00:28:15,503 --> 00:28:18,237
What a relief that I don't
have to give you a lift.

418
00:28:18,837 --> 00:28:20,570
Geez.

419
00:28:20,570 --> 00:28:23,071
He's always so snide.

420
00:28:23,071 --> 00:28:27,837
Mr. Na, I have an engagement
near the hospital. Could I get a lift?

421
00:28:27,837 --> 00:28:29,137
Bye.

422
00:28:29,937 --> 00:28:31,870
