428
00:28:46,837 --> 00:28:49,204
The insurance company
hooked me up with a rental car.

429
00:28:50,104 --> 00:28:52,404
I picked up a sweet ride.

430
00:28:52,404 --> 00:28:53,870
It's awesome.

431
00:28:55,004 --> 00:28:57,970
