434
00:29:11,171 --> 00:29:12,537
Do you suppose I would have carried it over?

435
00:29:12,537 --> 00:29:14,304
Are you nuts? You're too young to drive.

436
00:29:14,304 --> 00:29:16,637
I have a license. I used to drive
back in the States.

437
00:29:16,637 --> 00:29:18,137
This is Korea. Give me the key.

438
00:29:18,137 --> 00:29:19,704
- No. It's mine.
- Give it here.

439
00:29:19,704 --> 00:29:22,037
- It's mine.
- Hey!

440
00:29:22,037 --> 00:29:23,470
You're too young.

441
00:29:23,470 --> 00:29:24,603
Stop it. It's mine.

442
00:29:24,603 --> 00:29:25,904
Hey!

443
00:29:27,204 --> 00:29:28,670
No.

444
00:29:34,137 --> 00:29:36,137
How do you do, ma'am?

445
00:29:46,438 --> 00:29:47,804
It's nice to see you again.

446
00:29:47,804 --> 00:29:49,670
So you're back.

447
00:29:49,670 --> 00:29:53,371
