at my mom's restaurant.

469
00:31:23,837 --> 00:31:24,804
Give me the car key.

470
00:31:24,804 --> 00:31:25,804
No.

471
00:31:25,804 --> 00:31:27,704
Give it to me. The vice principal
is watching us.

472
00:31:34,670 --> 00:31:35,970
So long.

473
00:31:47,438 --> 00:31:50,171
What a relief. It's the same password.

474
00:31:50,171 --> 00:31:53,438
Wow. This dude sure has a lot of money!

475
00:31:54,171 --> 00:31:55,737
Luck you, Gil Teacher.

476
00:31:56,438 --> 00:32:00,470
I can close the deal on
our apartment with this.

477
00:32:00,470 --> 00:32:03,570
I thought we were going to lose
the deposit. What a relief.

478
00:32:04,204 --> 00:32:06,438
I should stay at that apartment.

479
00:32:06,438 --> 00:32:08,537
- Why?
- I almost got caught this morning.

480
00:32:08,537 --> 00:32:10,804
My uncle came by to clean the house.

481
00:32:10,804 --> 00:32:12,870
I guess he's decided to keep me around.

482
00:32:13,237 --> 00:32:18,704
But that apartment will be our marital home.

483
00:32:18,704 --> 00:32:23,438
I don't know about letting you move in.

484
00:32:24,704 --> 00:32:28,271
Should I have Yun Jae's precious body
sleeping on the streets?

485
00:32:29,737 --> 00:32:30,937
Fine.

486
00:32:30,937 --> 00:32:32,937
I'll let you use the smallest room.

487
00:32:32,937 --> 00:32:35,237
But my bed won't fit if the room is small.

488
00:32:35,237 --> 00:32:37,237
Your bed? You're bringing that, too?

489
00:32:37,237 --> 00:32:40,004
I can only fall asleep in that bed.

490
00:32:40,970 --> 00:32:43,037
Didn't you say we had a lot to do?

491
00:32:58,171 --> 00:33:01,470
These don't look like Gyeong Jun's clothes.

492
00:33:01,470 --> 00:33:02,770
Hon,

493
00:33:03,404 --> 00:33:05,004
whose shoes are these?

494
00:33:07,204 --> 00:33:08,837
