786
00:59:31,503 --> 00:59:35,870
We won't have to split anything

787
00:59:35,870 --> 00:59:37,870
if he comes by often, right?

788
00:59:37,870 --> 00:59:40,537
That's right. He can have the kimchi
whenever he comes over.

789
00:59:40,537 --> 00:59:42,438
He's closer by now.

790
00:59:42,438 --> 00:59:45,704
Tell him he's free to come over
whenever he wants to.

791
00:59:45,704 --> 00:59:47,104
Mom,

792
00:59:47,804 --> 00:59:54,171
what do you give someone if you want him
to feel free to come over whenever?

793
00:59:54,171 --> 00:59:56,204
Should we make Yun Jae a copy
of our house key?

794
00:59:56,204 --> 01:00:00,537
He can come by and eat
even if we're not around.

795
01:00:04,137 --> 01:00:06,237
Dad...

796
01:00:06,237 --> 01:00:10,104
Could you pull over? I have to go somewhere.

797
01:00:15,704 --> 01:00:17,338
Da Ran.

798
01:00:17,338 --> 01:00:18,837
Da Ran, where are you going?

799
01:00:24,937 --> 01:00:26,304
Hello?

800
01:00:26,304 --> 01:00:29,271
Yun Jae, is Da Ran there?

801
01:00:30,137 --> 01:00:32,071
No. Why?

802
01:00:32,071 --> 01:00:37,537
She asked dad to pull over
all of a sudden and then took off.

803
01:00:37,537 --> 01:00:39,204
It was odd.

804
01:00:43,104 --> 01:00:44,338
She's not picking up.

805
01:00:56,904 --> 01:00:58,937
I'm sorry to bother you,

806
01:00:58,937 --> 01:01:01,970
but Se Yeong lives near the hospital, right?

807
01:01:01,970 --> 01:01:05,037
Could I have her address?

808
01:02:57,737 --> 01:02:59,338
Who is it?

809
01:03:19,637 --> 01:03:20,937
Let go.

810
01:03:47,204 --> 01:03:48,570
[Big]

811
01:03:48,637 --> 01:03:51,570
How can you sit there
so brazen and shameless?

812
01:03:51,570 --> 01:03:54,338
When Yun Jae crashed into you,

813
01:03:54,338 --> 01:03:56,570
who do you suppose
he was in a hurry to get to?

814
01:03:58,037 --> 01:03:59,438
It should fit perfectly.

815
01:03:59,438 --> 01:04:02,271
The gentleman who ordered the ring
said he had the exact measurement.

816
01:04:02,271 --> 01:04:03,970
They're hiding something
so it doesn't show.

817
01:04:03,970 --> 01:04:05,904
They were arguing about whether
or not to go to the hospital.

818
01:04:09,271 --> 01:04:12,304
The patient who was brought here
with Kang Gyeong Jun

819
01:04:12,304 --> 01:04:13,438
was Seo Yun Jae?

820
01:04:13,438 --> 01:04:15,503
If you're going to take him down,
should I keep watch for you?

821
01:04:15,503 --> 01:04:16,937
No.

822
01:04:16,937 --> 01:04:19,371
I'm going to feign ignorance

823
01:04:19,371 --> 01:04:20,837
and just keep chugging along.
